ComicInfo.Summary:
Jungle Fantasy is back and delivering the steamiest action in the untamed wilds! Ivory has been through enough to break lesser women, but she continues her quest to find her child through all the terrors the jungle has thrown at her. Whether it is the primal lust of man or the instinctive hunger of the creatures that rule these jungles, she must not give in to the monsters that yearn to tear her apart. Boundless offers a host of sexy stunning covers with this issue including a Regular Cover by Renato Camilo, Wraparound Cover by Raulo Caceres, Natural Beauty Cover by Juan Jose Ryp, Luscious Cover by Matt Martin, and a Sultry Cover by Christian Zanier. Plus an array of super limited covers for the collector including a Century Nude (limited to 100 copies) by Gabriel Andrade, a Nude & Naughty Set (of 3 books) and a Costume Change Set (of 3 books), each limited to 250 sets, by Christian Zanier. And for the erotic art collectors, there is the Nude by Camilo, Sultry Nude by Zanier, Luscious Nude by Martin, Wraparound Nude Cover by Caceres, and Natural Beauty Stripping Cover by Juan Jose Ryp. For the best in erotic art we also have an Adult Cover and Adult Extreme Cover by artist Christian Zanier!
